Product Description

Welcome to our photography background store.

Backdrop parameters:
Name:Photography Backdrop
Material: Vinyl
Size: 5x3ft/150 x 100 cm
Pacakge: Only 1PC photo backdrop(Folding Shipping)

Features:
1. Digital computerprinted backdrop.high quality, vibrant color and very clear, Light weight and durable.
2. Vinyl cloth is not washable.Please use a damp cloth wipe the stain.
3. It is easy to fold, easy to carry, easy to hang up straightly or naturally.

How to use:
1.With the use of photographic stand, clips and light, the picture is better.
2.For family photography, Using tape to stick the backdrop to the wall.
3.It is better to keep some distance when you take pictures.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
